org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model
Class Component

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.XtalObject
      org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model.Component

public class Component
    
extends XtalObject





A class to describe a chemical component used in a Condition that makes
up a Crystallization Screen


Although this will not be strictly necessary for every condition, they
are likely to be stored in the database as reference data, so are unlikely to be
edited very often.


A component could be included in multiple Screen Conditions


A component will have its own safety information, which may or may not
affect the safety information of the Condition
